    narr:generatedFrom "e077f065177423d09a6eff0bb42bec11d953a02d" ;
    narr:narration """This hub tracks the evolution of audience-tailoring assessments, mapping how content adapts to distinct stakeholder needs. A primary cluster focuses on [technical fluency](narr:Assess_Tailoring_cm), where documents leverage [Git, RDF, and SPARQL](narr:RubricAssess_Tailoring_1) to signal domain expertise. A second, more expansive strand evaluates [explicit persona segmentation](narr:RubricAssess_tailoring), ranging from [multi-stakeholder address](narr:Assess_Tailoring_collective_memory) to formal [codification of audience segments](narr:RubricAssess_Tailoring). The third, enterprise-oriented trajectory examines the shift toward [executive-level communication](narr:Assessment_Tailoring_CustomerArchitect), specifically balancing [developer-first origins against strategic decision-maker requirements](narr:Assessment_Tailoring_IPCrisis). Recent assessments, such as [ADR-specific tailoring](narr:RubricAssess_Tailoring_ADR001) and [developer-tooling hooks](narr:RubricAssess_Tailoring_ADR002), highlight the tension between internal technical shorthand and the need for external translation. The collection remains split between documents that assume high-context familiarity and those actively building bridges to non-technical buyers through [GTM champion profiles](narr:RubricAssess_Tailoring_GTM).""" ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/ns/narrative#Assess_Tailoring_cm> ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/ns/narrative#Assess_Tailoring_collective_memory> ;
